Usage:
------

    ./update-routers.sh

Dependencies:
-------------

    rtrsub - https://github.com/job/rtrsub
    jinja2 - jinja.pocoo.org
    hiyapyco - https://pypi.python.org/pypi/HiYaPyCo
    bgpq3  - https://github.com/snar/bgpq3
